  "slug": "spiral-tower-villages",
  "title": "Lios Spiral Tower Villages",
  "description": "Adds unique towering villages with spiral layouts and distinct building styles",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/jktGQ4XC/Lios-Outlandish-Village-Spiral-Towers.png\" alt=\"Lios-Outlandish-Village-Spiral-Towers\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Spiral Tower Villages</strong>&nbsp;transforms your world with sky-reaching structures, custom surrounding worldgen, and layered mystery on every floor. Built long ago by villagers fleeing the dangers below, these vertical sanctuaries offered shelter&mdash;but not certainty. To protect their most prized possessions, they constructed hidden redstone mechanisms throughout. Secret triggers and concealed chambers now lie scattered across the towers, guarding rare loot and forgotten relics for the bold to uncover.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/lioloader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; text-decoration: none;\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wrK85wgc/logo.png\" alt=\"LioLoader\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" style=\"display:block; border-radius: 12px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.35;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: inherit;\">Need datapack-based configuration?</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.9;\">\n        Check out <strong>LioLoader</strong> for global datapack / resource pack loading. Available for <strong>NeoForge</strong> and <strong>Fabric</strong> on <strong>Minecraft 1.21.x</strong>.\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: inherit; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px;\">Open LioLoader on Modrinth →</div>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/9HZwsP9v/towers8.png\" alt=\"towers8\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/FqB3NwGL/towers3.png\" alt=\"towers3\" border=\"0\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/9kWBQpD5/towers7.png\" alt=\"towers7\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/HT8tF2By/towers1.png\" alt=\"towers1\" border=\"0\">  <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wNyQtsW3/towers2.png\" alt=\"towers2\" border=\"0\"> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/4w9qPp8C/towers9.png\" alt=\"towers9\" border=\"0\"> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/zT1pXxTy/towers4.png\" alt=\"towers4\" border=\"0\"> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/n2n5BVr/towers5.png\" alt=\"towers5\" border=\"0\"> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rGZW9xQb/towers10.png\" alt=\"towers10\" border=\"0\"> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/4njsCD1B/towers6.png\" alt=\"towers6\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/XrhYLBjD/compatibility.png\" alt=\"compatibility\" width=\"536\" height=\"49\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>These do not overhaul existing vanilla villages, making them compatible with any other village overhaul mod such as <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/lios-overhauled-villages\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Lio's Overhauled Villages</a>! Part of a new series, Lio's Outlandish Villages aims to bring uniquely styled towns and adventurous builds to explore!</em></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/RTMvjThM/features.png\" alt=\"features\" width=\"458\" height=\"62\" border=\"0\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Custom Loot Tables:</strong> Every chest is hand-tuned with unique rewards, offering a curated mix of useful gear, rare finds, and thematic items tailored to each tower.</li>\n<li><strong>Hidden Lore:</strong> Some chambers contain old villager diaries&mdash;written records that reveal fragments of their lives, the history of the towers, and the threats they once faced.</li>\n<li><strong>Highly Unique:</strong> With over 40 distinct tower variants in the generation pool, no two spiral villages are ever the same&mdash;each one offers a fresh layout and experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0phQs4Sb/morefromthisseries.png\" alt=\"morefromthisseries\" width=\"669\" height=\"57\" border=\"0\"> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/hobbit-hill-village\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NdsDc7TH/banner.png\" alt=\"banner\" width=\"345\" height=\"63\" border=\"0\"> </a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fV6VtS4Q/youtube-reviews.png\" alt=\"youtube-reviews\" width=\"605\" height=\"44\"></p>\n<details>\n<summary>Spoiler</summary>\n<p>-Reviewed At 11:31-<br><iframe title=\"TOP 20 NEW Minecraft Mods Of The Month! (1.21.7 to 1.20.1) | July\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/j5bxrkqWJkg?start=690\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>-Reviewed At 7:40-<br><div style=\"left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0; position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QxYuzW_sFMg?rel=0&start=465\" style=\"top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; position: absolute; border: 0;\" allowfullscreen scrolling=\"no\" allow=\"accelerometer *; clipboard-write *; encrypted-media *; gyroscope *; picture-in-picture *; web-share *;\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\"></iframe></div>\n</details>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/pGkUmgGcsY\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qDNhg49/636e0a6a49cf127bf92de1e2-icon-clyde-blurple-RGB.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"97\"></a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\">Usage in Modpacks</span></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Feel free to include the <strong>Spiral Tower Villages</strong> in any Minecraft modpack of your choice. We encourage you to build unique and engaging adventures by incorporating these vertical village structures into your customized packs. No need to request permission&mdash;just explore and enjoy the village towers however you like!</p>",
